---
title: Double American-Style & Mustard Sauce with Creamy Onion Mash
description: Long after you finish this dinner of steak and three veg, you're going to remember the way it was transformed by the simple addition
of a luscious mustard sauce. It's an easy trick that gives this classic dish a new lease of life.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/double-southern-steak-mustard-sauce-c3cbc909.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/double-southern-steak-mustard-sauce-61692cee8a7a5b0c4319d8d2-68f387dc.pdf
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipes/double-american-style-and-mustard-sauce-61692cee8a7a5b0c4319d8d2
course: main course
cuisine: North America
time required: 40 minutes
